---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Amicbridge">
  <section class="min-h-screen bg-transparent text-gray-100 py-20 px-6 sm:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        Empowering People to <span class="text-blue-400">Own the Future</span> of Finance
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-200 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Amicbridge is a trusted platform built for the next generation of ownership — 
        where everyday people can tokenize real-world assets and share their value with others. 
        We exist to bring fairness, transparency, and opportunity to private finance through verified digital asset networks.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-20 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div class="bg-[#1b2a3a]/70 p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-[#2f3a48]">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
          Our mission is simple: to make ownership and investment accessible to everyone. 
          We’re creating a global platform where people can tokenize property, businesses, 
          vehicles, or creative projects — and verified investors can participate directly. 
          By replacing gatekeepers with technology, Amicbridge helps wealth flow freely, safely, and transparently between people.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-[#1b2a3a]/70 p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-[#2f3a48]">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Our Promise</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
          We don’t control your funds or take hidden fees. Every transaction is peer-to-peer, 
          powered by verified identity and blockchain accountability. 
          Our one-time membership model ensures that Amicbridge serves the community — 
          not the other way around. Your data, your asset, your control.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Vision -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-24 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Our Vision: A World of Shared Ownership</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-200 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        Imagine a world where you can own part of a city apartment, a piece of a renewable energy farm, or 
        a share in an independent business — all from your phone. 
        Amicbridge makes that possible by transforming assets into verified digital tokens 
        that can be invested in, traded, and trusted globally.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Values -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white text-center mb-12">Our Core Values</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
        <div class="bg-[#1b2a3a]/60 p-8 rounded-xl border border-[#2f3a48] hover:border-blue-500 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-3">Transparency</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-200">
            Every transaction on Amicbridge is traceable and verified — we believe visibility builds confidence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#1b2a3a]/60 p-8 rounded-xl border border-[#2f3a48] hover:border-blue-500 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-3">Trust & Verification</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-200">
            All users and assets go through a verification process, ensuring the integrity of every deal on our network.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#1b2a3a]/60 p-8 rounded-xl border border-[#2f3a48] hover:border-blue-500 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-3">Innovation for People</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-200">
            Finance should empower, not exclude. Our technology exists to make 
            investing and ownership simple, human, and borderless.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Trust & Safety -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-24 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Trust & Safety First</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-200 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        ✅ All members are identity-verified by Amicbridge. <br/>
        🔒 Peer-to-peer transactions — your funds stay in your control. <br/>
        🧾 One-time access fee — no ongoing commissions or hidden terms. <br/>
        🌍 Built on blockchain transparency — visible, secure, and fair.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Founder Section -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-24 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Leadership</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-200 mb-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Amicbridge is led by <span class="font-semibold text-blue-400">robert frame</span>, 
        a visionary entrepreneur based in Oslo, Norway. His goal is to make private finance 
        open, fair, and powered by people — not institutions.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-300">
        📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Oslo, Norway<br/>
        📞 <strong>Phone:</strong> +47 92928373
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Be Part of the Ownership Revolution</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-200 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Join Amicbridge and help build a fairer, people-powered financial network.  
        Tokenize your assets or invest in verified projects — safely, transparently, and globally.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-10 py-4 bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-full shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
